he Father, by Enrique Buenaventura (Colombia); The Mulatto’s Orgy, by Luisa Josefina Hernández (Mexico); and Viña: Three Beach Plays, by Sergio Vodánovic (Chile).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aSpanish American drama-Translations into English. 7aDRAMA / General.2bisacsh1 aBuenaventura, Enrique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCarballido, Emilio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGambaro, Griselda, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJosefina Hernandez, Luisa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMaggi, Carlos, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOliver, William I., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aVodánovic, Sergio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/70123640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781477304549423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781477304549/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK